description: Data was generated from file metadata information from the GDC legacy archive release 15, February 2019. More details: https://docs.gdc.cancer.gov/Data/Release_Notes/Data_Release_Notes/#data-release-150

fields.description: Referring to the default/main database at the GDC. In this table, this field is always legacy.
fields.name: dbName

fields.description: Unique GDC identifier for this file (corresponds to the file_barcode)  --  this can be used to access more information from the GDC data portal like this: https://portal.gdc.cancer.gov/files/c21b332c-06c6-4403-9032-f91c8f407ba1
fields.name: file_gdc_id

fields.description: Data accessibility policy (open or controlled)
fields.name: access

fields.description: Access Control List -- if access is controlled, this field contains the dbGaP accession, eg phs000179
fields.name: acl

fields.description: GDC archive UUID
fields.name: archive_gdc_id

fields.description: Archive revision number
fields.name: archive_revision

fields.description: Archive state
fields.name: archive_state

fields.description: Original archive submitter name, eg  nationwidechildrens.org_BRCA.bio.Level_1.56
fields.name: archive_submitter_id

fields.description: GDC case uuid for associated case(s)
fields.name: associated_entities__case_gdc_id

fields.description: GDC entity uuid for associated entity(ies)
fields.name: associated_entities__entity_gdc_id

fields.description: Submitter id for associated entity(ies)
fields.name: associated_entities__entity_submitter_id

fields.description: Associated entity type, eg   aliquot   or   case
fields.name: associated_entities__entity_type

fields.description: GDC unique identifier
fields.name: case_gdc_id

fields.description: Program dbGaP accession number, eg phs000183
fields.name: project_dbgap_accession_number

fields.description: The type of disease studied by the project; eg. Sarcoma,  Breast Invasive Carcinoma,Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia, etc
fields.name: project_disease_type

fields.description: Project Name; frequently the same as or similar to the project disease type eg   Acute Lymphoblastic Leukemia - Phase II   or   Breast Invasive Carcinoma   etc
fields.name: project_name

fields.description: Program dbGaP accession number, eg phs000178
fields.name: program_dbgap_accession_number

fields.description: Program name, eg TCGA or TARGET
fields.name: program_name

fields.description: Project name abbreviation; the program name appended with a project name abbreviation; eg. TCGA-OV, etc.
fields.name: project_short_name

fields.description: One of CGC, GSC, BCR, COM (or null)
fields.name: center_type

fields.description: TCGA codes for the Professional Organization or Group (Center) which has submitted the data, more info: https://gdc.cancer.gov/resources-TCGA-users/TCGA-code-tables/center-codes
fields.name: center_code

fields.description: Center name, eg BCM, BI, WUGSC
fields.name: center_name

fields.description: Center abbreviation, eg WUSM
fields.name: center_short_name

fields.description: Timestamp of creation, eg 2016-10-27T21:58:12.297090-05:07
fields.name: created_datetime

fields.description: Category description of the underlying data, eg Clinical, Raw Sequencing Data, Simple Nucleotide Variation, Transcriptome Profiling  , etc
fields.name: data_category

fields.description: File format of the underlying data, eg BCR XML, BAM
fields.name: data_format

fields.description: Experimental source of the data type, eg Tissue slide image, RNA-Seq
fields.name: data_type

fields.description: Experimental strategy used to generate data (where applicable) e.g. WXS, RNA-Seq
fields.name: experimental_strategy

fields.description: Name of file at the GDC
fields.name: file_name

fields.description: The size of a file measured in bytes (B), kilobytes (KB), megabytes (MB), gigabytes (GB), terabytes (TB), and larger values.
fields.name: file_size

fields.description: GDC file identifier. This is a duplicate of file_gdc_id field found in some tables.
fields.name: file_id

fields.description: Where available, GDC file uuid for index file
fields.name: index_file_gdc_id

fields.description: Where available, GDC file name for index file
fields.name: index_file_name

fields.description: Where available, size of the index file in bytes
fields.name: index_file_size

fields.description: Md5sum for GDC data file
fields.name: md5sum

fields.description: GDC file UUID for metadata (eg mage-tab) file
fields.name: metadata_file_id

fields.description: Name of GDC metadata file
fields.name: metadata_file_name

fields.description: Size of metadata file
fields.name: metadata_file_size

fields.description: Type of metadata file, eg mage-tab
fields.name: metadata_file_type

fields.description: Platform used to generate this data, eg  Illumina  , or  Affymetrix SNP 6.7
fields.name: platform

fields.description: File state -- either live or submitted
fields.name: file_state

fields.description: Original submitter file id (eg CGHub analysis_id)
fields.name: file_submitter_id

fields.description: Semicolon-delimited list of file tags, eg  coverage  , or  hg19;nocnv  , etc
fields.name: file_tags

fields.description: File Type  -- eg aligned_reads , simple_somatic_mutation , gene_expression , etc
fields.name: file_type

fields.description: Timestamp of latest update, eg 2017-03-04T16:37:26.081298-06:00
fields.name: updated_datetime
